Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.35,0:00:08.26,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,I tol' ya, it don' matter where ya came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.56,0:00:10.72,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,What matters is where ya wanna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:15.45,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,You just said that. \NShe's heavy in more than one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:17.45,Shibasaki_00:15(Ep 07),Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Shibasaki
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:20.66,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Shibasaki, we're here. Do you have your key?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.82,0:00:22.87,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Key?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.04,0:00:24.83,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Key...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:28.04,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.77,0:00:33.71,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear, Kazu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:37.14,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Look at you, not answering your \Nphone and blubbering drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.36,0:00:40.66,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:15.61,Ep_Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(650,1)}#07 Curious Chitose and Parents' Day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:16.43,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Oh? My, my, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.43,0:02:19.61,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen you on that TV thing before!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.59,0:02:21.48,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:24.87,Theory_02:21(Ep 07),Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Theory of Acting and Drama
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.44,0:02:24.87,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for bringing her home. \NSorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:26.12,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,It's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.47,0:02:27.92,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.92,0:02:29.28,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:32.24,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'd be surprised if you show up \Non TV wearing a swimsuit like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:34.90,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Your father's very worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:39.05,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Were we on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:40.80,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,She probably meant the bonus footage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:41.34,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:02:45.56,Default - Italics,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,My grandma also calls any \Nkind of video footage "TV."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:47.16,Default - Italics,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful, old-timey Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:49.06,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:51.40,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kazu-chan, where are your tea cups for guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:53.24,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:56.10,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But what do you do when you have friends over?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:58.55,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. It's not like anyone comes over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:00.04,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:04.32,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Your clothes will get wrinkled if you \Ndon't change. Did you take off your makeup?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:09.70,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:12.50,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't mind us. We'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:23.51,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Shibasaki-san doesn't have any friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:25.02,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,You don't, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:26.60,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:28.47,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:32.79,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,She's been like that ever since \Nshe came here from Yamagata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:36.06,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Must be rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:40.16,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,It's rough for everyone. \NThat's just how this industry is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:42.96,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Right? So true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:46.78,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,My parents were against me \Nbecoming a voice actress, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:48.58,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:51.37,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,I see... It's normal for parents to oppose that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:52.77,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:55.00,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Gojo-kun was also a voice actor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.63,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,We had seen some of the \Nharsh realities of it already,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:59.75,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,so they tried even harder to discourage me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:00.67,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.84,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Er... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:08.93,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? My taxi fare...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.77,Default,Towa,0000,0000,0000,,After the jingle will be listener messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:15.73,Default,Towa,0000,0000,0000,,We've picked out some messages, \Nso please read them in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.01,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:21.06,Default - Italics,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Two, four, six, eight... \Nwho do we appreciate...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:22.98,Default - Italics,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,We're gradually getting fewer messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:24.96,Default - Italics,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,The number of plays is also down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:27.76,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Heyo! What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:29.74,Default,Towa,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare for you to show up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:32.47,Default,Kzu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be in the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:35.54,Default,Towa,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should show up on site more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:38.55,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's hard being there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:40.25,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you've got a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:42.55,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:47.69,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:52.23,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:55.37,Default,Mm,0000,0000,0000,,I went to say hello at your office,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:57.51,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,and they asked if I wanted to come see you work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.72,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:04.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, your mom was worried \Nabout your work, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.83,Default,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Then you could have at least told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:08.07,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Hello, hello, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:10.45,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Please come over here so you can watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:10.66,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,No, she'll be leaving right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:13.48,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Why, thank you, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:15.00,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He's the P of this series.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:15.67,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,P?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:17.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He's the producer. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:19.92,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You could say he's a very \Nimportant business partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.41,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:24.08,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful for someone \Nwho looks so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:26.66,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... Well, you might say
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:28.52,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,this is a very merit-based business,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:31.00,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,so age really means very little...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:33.18,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. I'm the producer, Kuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:35.31,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for taking such \Ngood care of my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:36.13,Default,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Hey—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:39.06,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,For me? Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:41.77,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Towada, get her some tea. Some for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:42.88,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:43.61,Default,Towa,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:45.61,Default,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please just stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.90,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kazu-chan, would you please \Nhand these out to everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:49.07,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,There's one for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:51.92,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,This is embarrassing! \NYou're embarrassing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:52.89,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You've got a nice mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:01.67,Interview_05:58(Ep 07),Pink,0000,0000,0000,,An Interview With Torimaru Chitose-san, Who Plays the Main \NHeroine Yuna in "Millennium Princess x Kowloon Overlord"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:01.67,Default,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Torimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.84,Parents'_Day_06:03(Ep 07),Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Shibasaki-san's experiencing Parents' \NDay at work right now lolololololol
