Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.84,Read(bottom)_06:03(Ep 07),Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Read
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:11.22,Work_06:09(Ep 07),Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Work{\c&H85796D&}, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:15.18,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,How is this a radio program? CooS Radio!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:19.19,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,This program is brought to you by...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.66,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,...Peitax Entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:24.21,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,We've got all of the heroines here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:26.74,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Yae-chan, who plays Mao, and Koto-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:28.61,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,who plays Ria, are joining us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:32.37,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kugayama Yae, and I play Mao. \NTh-Thank you for having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:35.58,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, everyone! \NI'm Katakura Koto, and I play Ria.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.03,0:06:39.79,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, the studio seems much \Nsmaller with all of us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:41.08,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,It feels so crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:42.74,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry Yae's taking up so much room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:44.04,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,Chi-chan, do you want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:47.05,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man... It's only been five seconds,\Nand we already have to cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:50.26,Default,Kzu,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, we're going to have \Nto redo that from the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:53.03,Default,Towa,0000,0000,0000,,All right, here we go again from the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:56.26,Default,Towa,0000,0000,0000,,Five, four, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:03.98,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,All right, next up is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:04.77,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Listener messages!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:07.20,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,We've got lots of messages again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:08.24,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:11.60,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Kusure name, \N"Chinese Fried Sesame Dumpling-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:14.58,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,"CooS evening, everyone." Yes, CooS evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.04,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,CooS evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:18.42,Default - Italics,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I can't get used to this stupid greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:19.11,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm the one who recently asked you if
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:21.40,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,I should confess my love \Nfor my childhood friend."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.50,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's the person who sent us\Na message two episodes ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:26.43,Default - Italics,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You're amazing... Are you \Nactually watching this anime?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:26.88,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,"All of you cheered me on,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.43,0:07:28.14,Default - Italics,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Are you a fan? Are you actually a fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:30.70,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't work up the courage because I'm \Nafraid it might ruin our current friendship."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:31.71,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,I totally get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:35.14,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,"So I was wondering if I could get some \Nwords of encouragement from you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:37.43,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care, \Nand keep up the good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.43,Default,Mmo,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.99,0:07:41.14,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,There are things you can't say, \Nhowever badly you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:44.90,Default - Italics,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Totally. "You're being dramatic. \NYou're laying it on as much as Yae does."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:44.90,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,But you might regret it if you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:46.97,Default - Italics,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}That's one thing I could never say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:47.78,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Since you've known each \Nother for more than ten years,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:49.14,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:51.08,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:53.24,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,So, Chinese Fried Sesame Dumpling-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:54.70,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:01.21,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,The next message we have is from
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:03.33,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Kusure name "Tunamayo-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:06.04,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Is that their favorite rice ball filling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:10.01,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,"Nice to meet you. I'm a second-year \Nin high school, and I love anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:13.26,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,After I graduate, I'm planning to go \Nto Tokyo and become a voice actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:16.99,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Why did all of you decide \Nto become voice actors?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:17.93,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,You, Koto-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:21.18,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,I've always liked anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:23.39,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,and before I knew it, \NI'd decided I would be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:25.07,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you took that route?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:28.42,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the same. The "I thought \NI could just become one" route.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:30.45,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, isn't that different? \NI'm not sure that's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:32.16,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's totally the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:34.53,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Someone in my family was doing this job,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:36.28,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought that I could do it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:40.39,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,So I was influenced by those around me \Nand my surroundings. You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:41.75,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:44.10,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,See? That does happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:45.75,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Was it the same for you, Momoka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:47.94,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:51.78,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well... I guess that was part of it, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:53.05,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Kazuha-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:56.74,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to become an actress,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:59.02,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,and I liked acting and anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:01.47,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,so I decided that was what I wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:03.39,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:04.73,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:07.20,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you like it and want to do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:09.07,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,if there's no one who understands you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:09.94,Don't_09:07(Ep 07),Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go too far
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:11.40,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,and if your surroundings won't allow it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:14.77,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also not from Tokyo, \Njust like Tunamayo-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:16.91,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,so I know how hard that can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:19.88,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of hurdles \Nthat you have to get over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:24.08,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,So prepare as much as you can right now, \Nand make your dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:25.37,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be cheering you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:27.33,Be_Nice!_09:25(Ep 07),Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Be gentle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:29.25,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. There are a lot of difficult things,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:31.14,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,but there are a lot of fun things, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:32.80,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I totally get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,0:09:36.68,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Right... Well, there's a lot to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:40.02,Default,Mmo,0000,0000,0000,,This turned out to be a really good talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:42.56,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we supposed to go after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:45.37,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,And with that, we've reached the end \Nof our listener message segment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:47.25,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,So dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:48.75,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,I am not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:58.55,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,So you're finally on the side of cheering \Nother people on with their dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:00.80,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I was a bit moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:02.98,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,I just said what they wanted to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:04.58,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:05.29,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:09.83,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, this is my job. \NI'm not doing anything weird, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:14.25,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I mean, this is just for \Npromotion and isn't actual acting...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:16.58,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,But this is part of my job, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:18.25,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,And that swimsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:19.63,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That was also for promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:21.82,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But seeing that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:23.68,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,That was my first and last time in a swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:24.71,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:26.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We should probably be a bit \Nmore flexible there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:28.67,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,It was the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:29.14,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.78,0:10:33.11,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You seem more cheerful \Nthan I thought. I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:35.40,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,And you seem to have some wonderful friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:39.91,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:42.49,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,You're in front of the exit, \Nso we couldn't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:43.55,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:44.30,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:46.36,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, now. It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:48.66,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know all the details, \Nbut we can't help being curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:52.05,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kazu-chan, Kazu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:53.15,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.34,Cell_Phone(Ep 07),Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Dad\N{\fs16}Incoming Call...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:10:59.26,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Let your father hear how well you're doing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:01.60,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:03.47,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Here? Right now? Is this thing connected?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:04.93,Cell_Phone(Ep 07),Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Dad\N{\fs16}Incoming Call...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:05.85,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes. It is a phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:07.86,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:13.21,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing to say to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:14.63,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:17.57,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Your father was most worried \Nafter he saw you in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:19.68,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,I told you about the swimsuit already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:21.03,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing more to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:25.22,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Hmm? Foom, foom, foom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:29.75,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I heard everything, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:32.61,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Leave everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:33.46,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:34.58,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.58,0:11:36.10,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hello. This is Kuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:38.25,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you could say that \NI'm in charge of this anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:41.09,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuha-chan's been doing great work for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:45.07,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'm not the only admiring her great work. \NAll the young men in the country are, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:46.51,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:50.95,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Really, sir, Kazuha-chan is the \Nultimate presence to give
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:54.10,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,hopes, dreams, and comfort to \Nyoung and mature men alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:56.90,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Especially the presence of her breasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:59.65,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,And so, as you can see, we'll take responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.95,0:12:02.26,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes... Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:05.19,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hand you over to the one in charge...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:07.80,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Towada! Towada!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:09.29,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:12.34,Default,Towa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:13.71,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:14.85,Default,Toaw,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:15.61,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:16.92,Default,Towa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:21.31,Default,Towa,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, this is Towada of Peitax...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:24.80,Default,Towa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Kuzu is my boss... Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:26.43,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Seems Papa's a little angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:29.10,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm sure he is. Probably super pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:29.10,Default,Towa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:31.93,Default,Towa,0000,0000,0000,,I am so very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:34.66,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzu-san, what are you \Ngoing to do about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:35.60,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Tee-hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:39.46,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If Shibasaki's work is hindered at all, \Nit'll be a huge loss for our agency!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:42.40,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. I'll make sure \NTowada works things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:45.49,Default,Towa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:49.06,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be sure to make it up to you soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:50.50,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,so please tell your husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:52.66,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry about that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:55.00,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:56.38,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,You should just leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:57.32,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kazu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:13:00.78,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, your body may have grown, \Nbut you're still such a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:03.81,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Your father's not always \Ngoing to be well, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:04.17,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:06.68,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be heading home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:08.86,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to make the shinkansen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:10.11,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:13.73,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I am a proprietress, and leaving all the \Nwork to your father is hard on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:16.75,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so busy, you could have just called.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:20.15,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of things I can find out \Njust by seeing your face, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:22.10,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:25.07,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:27.53,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.27,0:13:31.95,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,She's a great mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:33.70,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:39.36,Default,Towa,0000,0000,0000,,Shibasaki-san, I think it'd be a good idea
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:41.23,Default,Towa,0000,0000,0000,,for us to go apologize in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:44.15,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Right. We'll make it a day when\Nyou're off, so you should...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:45.17,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.43,0:13:48.28,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But it'd be a bit awkward if it was just us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:50.26,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,So he {\i1}was{\i0} angry, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:52.53,Default,Towa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if "angry" is the word...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:54.16,Default,Towa,0000,0000,0000,,He was just very intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:56.78,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's the thing with Kuzu-san, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:14:00.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,but we should get him to understand \Nabout the swimsuit and your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:02.85,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If he were to show up on site...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:05.34,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,But it's pretty far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:07.87,Default,Kzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's half a day away from Tokyo, \Nand it's in the mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:11.45,Default,Kzu,0000,0000,0000,,So we'd have to stay at least a night, \Nor at most, three nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:12.17,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:14.20,Default,Tow,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you're planning to go with us, Kuzu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:16.69,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a choice. I'm the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:18.59,Default,Towa,0000,0000,0000,,No, we'll handle it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:21.13,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know. I totally understand that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:23.20,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,you don't want to trouble me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:26.06,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the producer's job to put out any fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:28.07,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzu-san, I'll go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:31.35,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just stand by when \Nmy friend is in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.69,0:14:33.81,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Right! That's the obvious thing to feel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:37.18,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! I'm the lead on this show, so I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:40.92,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Well said! Chi-sama knows exactly \Nwhat it means to be at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:42.23,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's all go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:44.73,Default,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Hot springs, here we come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:47.19,Default,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Karasuma Chitose will do her best!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:49.63,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Chi-sama, we see right through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:51.16,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Gojo-san's gonna yell at you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:53.17,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. It's for work, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.17,0:14:55.28,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,Chi-chan, we shouldn't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:57.12,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going, Yae? But hot \Nsprings help you lose weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:58.06,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:01.46,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,That's not okay! And I won't lose any weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:02.84,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:04.73,Default,Towa,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Great job today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:07.59,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry. Today was, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:10.13,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,No, today was a very valuable experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.59,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Great job, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:21.61,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna hang out with me for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:28.16,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuha-sama, here's your drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:29.70,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:34.62,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,That's the stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:39.67,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzu P and Chi-sama sure \Ndo go above and beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:41.50,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,In all the wrong ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.62,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Work is going to be awkward from tomorrow on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:46.40,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they don't say anything weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:47.59,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:50.86,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Chi-sama doesn't have much interest in others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:53.82,Default,Kooto,0000,0000,0000,,The other two aren't the type to say anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:55.05,Default,Kooto,0000,0000,0000,,and neither am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:15:57.82,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:01.09,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,So, are you going to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:02.55,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:03.65,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:05.74,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,How long has it been since you were home?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:08.29,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,About five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:11.44,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,It might be quite the surprise, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:15.19,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,True... Since I left home with \Nthe intention of never going back,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:16.84,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they'd be quite surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:20.05,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. I mean you're going \Nto be surprised, Kazuha-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:20.62,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.13,0:16:24.20,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Parents tend to get smaller \Nthe longer you don't see them,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:26.60,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,and they aren't as young as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:28.09,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:30.90,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my parents are just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:32.55,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:37.52,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,But when I go home once in a while, \NI'm always surprised at how much they've aged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:45.44,Default,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:47.60,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! I'm the leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:50.65,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,The chairman! I have to go to \Nmy friends when they're in need!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:52.87,Default,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Then support them at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:56.10,Default,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, you're the one \Nholding everyone back the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:58.62,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,But Kuzu-san said we should all go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:01.79,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Since it was an order from the producer,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:04.33,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't that make this work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:05.09,Default,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:07.76,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! I don't have any work anyway, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:11.17,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a crappy, small-fry newbie with no work, \Nso I have all the free time in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:13.88,Default,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say something that \Nembarrassing so confidently?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.88,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go to the hot springs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:19.44,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't have good days once in a while, \NI'm not going to feel like working.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:21.35,Default,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}If you have that much free time, \Nreview your scripts more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:24.81,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagata's a great place. Let's go once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:28.27,Default,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Food, transportation, lodging, and gifts...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:31.17,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna expense them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:34.23,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Gonna eat Yamagata steak, \Nsukiyaki, and shabu-shabu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:36.70,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go! I wanna eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:39.53,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:42.49,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:45.32,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Morning. Are you voicing another character?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:45.87,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:49.71,Default,Mane,0000,0000,0000,,We seem to be running into you \Na lot lately, Kugayama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:53.65,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes! They've been letting me \Ndo all kinds of roles lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:55.75,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure to work with you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:17:58.75,Default,Manee,0000,0000,0000,,That Karasuma from Number One \NProduce isn't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:01.54,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike the other Karasuma \Nfrom Number One Produce.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:04.89,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, b-but they might be implementing \Neven more new characters,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:06.30,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,so maybe Chi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:07.35,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.66,0:18:09.83,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Also, why are you being so formal with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:11.32,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that wasn't necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:15.78,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, you are my senpai, Sono-san, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.92,Default,Sono,0000,0000,0000,,You really are completely \Ndifferent from Chitose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:21.58,Default,Sono,0000,0000,0000,,You can just call me Momoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:23.33,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:23.70,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:24.66,Sono-1_18:23(Ep 07),Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Sono Momoka-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.55,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me feel more at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:35.34,Default,Mane,0000,0000,0000,,Kugayama-san, would you \Nlike something to dri—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:40.30,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,To be able to call you by your first name...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:42.83,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like we're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:45.28,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,You really do get pitiful at times...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:49.79,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... It's just that in an anime I liked,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:51.95,Default,Ye,0000,0000,0000,,they call each other by their last names,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:53.80,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,but then there's a scene \Nwhere they use first names,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:56.53,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,and you feel like they really became friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:59.12,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, {\i1}Pure Para{\i0}. So you saw that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:00.33,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.33,0:19:01.69,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:04.59,Default,Yaee,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! Sono Sakura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:08.83,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,I've always liked them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:11.04,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pure Para{\i0} and Sono Sakura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:17.96,Default,Mane,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can probably look forward \Nto the next series, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:20.89,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really? Is it that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:22.77,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,What will the toys be like this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:25.14,Default,Mane,0000,0000,0000,,Er... I just heard a little something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:26.96,Default,Mane,0000,0000,0000,,You know, l-like a rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:30.60,Default,Yae,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait! I wonder which \Nvoice actors are going to be in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:34.75,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pure Para{\i0}, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:39.07,Sono-2_19:36(Ep 07),Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Sono Momoka-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:45.03,Sono-3_19:39(Ep 07),Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Sono Momoka-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:47.49,Default - Italics,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,We'll never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:49.47,Default - Italics,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to protect everyone's smiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:50.87,Default - Italics,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:52.92,Default - Italics,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... I'll do my best, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:54.85,Default - Italics,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.33,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:56.86,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:02.31,Default - Italics,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:04.81,Default - Italics,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... I'll do my best, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.81,0:20:06.49,Default - Italics,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.53,0:20:09.98,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:12.31,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nah, I was gonna head to bed anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:12.81,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:14.97,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:18.15,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,That swimsuit thing was pretty well-received,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:20.42,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,and I got some offers \Nto do some gravure stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:23.20,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I can't say I'm very fond of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.98,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,So you're against it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:26.28,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:28.83,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,If it's something you want \Nto try, I won't stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:35.82,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're popular for your pure and cute image,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:38.80,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,so I just thought it'd be better if \Nyou didn't stray too far from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:41.86,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It probably won't go over very well \Nwith the {\i1}Pure Para{\i0} audience, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:46.23,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right. I guess my \Nimage is important, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:49.93,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, it's your decision to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:52.36,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're already a professional, Momoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:54.31,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:55.58,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Well, goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.86,0:21:13.13,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,So stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:18.79,Hey_21:15(Ep 07),Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,\NYou might have already heard from your mom, but the dinner meeting for \NPure Para's been scheduled, so I'm contacting you. I'll send you the details \Nin another message, so make sure you look at it. They seem pretty excited \Nabout this and might have invited too many people. Well, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:20.79,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hear anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:23.26,If_you're_late_21:22(Ep 07),Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo Station at 7:00 AM!!\NIf you're late, you're gonna buy me a drink!!\NI'm so excited!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:24.38,If_you're_late_21:22(Ep 07),Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Hot springs! Table tennis! Pillow fights! \NInn food that you can eat for free is so good!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:29.18,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,She's so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:30.06,Idiot_21:29(Ep 07),Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:30.72,Thanks_21:30(Ep 07),Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:31.64,Night_21:30(Ep 07),Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Night~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:33.89,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,So am I, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.85,0:21:43.45,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:47.34,Default,Chit,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have work. \NI don't have work forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:51.31,Default - MC,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,The Yamagata-bound
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:57.09,Default - MC,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,shinkansen Tsubasa 128 leaving at 7:28
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:59.34,Default,Kuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Morning! Look, I bought some Jet shumai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:59.34,Default - MC,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,will be arriving shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.34,0:22:03.55,Tsubasa_21:59(Ep 07),Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubasa\N137
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.34,0:22:03.55,Yama|Shin_21:59(Ep 07),Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagata | Shinjo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.81,0:22:01.95,Default,Towa,0000,0000,0000,,I booked us some seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.95,0:22:03.09,Default,Mane,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:05.26,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:06.47,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:09.47,Default,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,What's that dumb look for? Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:24:09.42,Preview,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.24,0:23:41.78,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.78,0:23:43.90,Default,who,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Yamagata's famous for its hot springs!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.90,0:23:45.67,Default,Who,0000,0000,0000,,It's great for your skin and detoxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.67,0:23:47.46,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,No way it's really that effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.46,0:23:50.40,Default,Who,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see what a body that grew up \Nin a hot springs inn looks like!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.40,0:23:52.08,Default,Who,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? It's actually pretty voluptuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.08,0:23:54.37,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:56.43,Default,Who,0000,0000,0000,,Take that, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.38,0:24:00.41,Default,Kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone actually have \Ntrash conversations like this?
